io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.player.highlight

Class BlockHighlightCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.player.callback.BlockHighlightCallback
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FrameCallback, FrameCallbackAttribute, BlockHighlightCallbackPrototype

    public final class BlockHighlightCallback
extends java.lang.Object
implements BlockHighlightCallbackPrototype
    The callback used to update block highlights for each frame when necessary.

    This video player is only visible if the player has debug mode turned on. It uses custom packets to send to the player with the RGB colors to make a video player.
